songs.title: Amerika
songs.lyrics:
I love my country and the president
I love my people and their ways
I love the mountains and the big blue lakes
I never ever wanna leave

My country tis of thee
Sweet land of twits and freaks
Anything that you wanna be
You can be in my country

America
My country
My mommy
America

America
My country
My mommy
America

I love the midwest and the weirdos
I love the piggies and the corn
I love the city and the hot dogs
I love Creedence and The Ramones

My country tis of thee
Sweet land of punks and geeks
How good it is to be
Free to eat bologna

America
My country
Bologna
America

America
My country
My mommy
My mommy
